    <string name="about_us" translatable="false"><![CDATA[
        <h3>Welcome to Deen Azkar</h3>
        <p><b>Deen Azkar</b> is your daily companion for spiritual growth and religious mindfulness. Our mission is to provide an accessible and comprehensive resource for Muslims worldwide to practice their faith with ease and precision.</p>

        <h4>Key Features:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Daily Azkar:</b> A vast collection of authentic Duas and Adkhar from Hisnul Muslim, categorized for every occasion.</li>
            <li><b>Prayer Times:</b> Accurate local prayer timings with notifications to help you stay connected to your salah.</li>
            <li><b>Zakat Calculator:</b> An easy-to-use tool for calculating your Zakat based on net assets and current Nisab thresholds.</li>
            <li><b>Hijrah Calendar:</b> Stay updated with Islamic dates and important events throughout the Hijri year.</li>
            <li><b>Bookmarks:</b> Save your favorite Duas for quick access whenever you need them.</li>
            <li><b>Night Mode:</b> Comfortable reading experience in low-light environments.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>This application is designed with simplicity and authenticity in mind. We strive to provide accurate content sourced from reliable Islamic references.</p>

        <p>For feedback or suggestions, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:developerussy@gmail.com">developerussy@gmail.com</a></p>

        <p><i>May Allah (SWT) accept our efforts and make this app a source of benefit for the Ummah.</i></p>
    ]]></string>

